# .trivyignore
# Trivy ignore file for known acceptable findings
# https://aquasecurity.github.io/trivy/latest/docs/configuration/filtering/

# ECS Fargate tasks need HTTPS (443) egress to 0.0.0.0/0 to reach
# ECR (pull images), SNS (publish messages), and CloudWatch (logs).
# Restricting to VPC endpoints would add cost/complexity for a dev assessment.
AVD-AWS-0104

# CloudFront uses the default *.cloudfront.net certificate which only
# supports minimum_protocol_version = "TLSv1". Setting TLSv1.2 requires
# a custom domain + ACM certificate. Acceptable for this assessment.
AVD-AWS-0013

# Bootstrap S3 bucket uses AWS-managed KMS (sse_algorithm = "aws:kms")
# instead of customer-managed key. AWS-managed KMS is acceptable for
# Terraform state bucket in this assessment context.
AVD-AWS-0132
